1
00:00:06,388 --> 00:00:08,920
We have the results of the guest survey.
我们有了顾客调查的结果.

2
00:00:08,921 --> 00:00:10,229
The good news is,
好消息是,

3
00:00:10,230 --> 00:00:13,460
our guests think we do a very good job.
我们的顾客认为我们干得很棒.

4
00:00:13,461 --> 00:00:16,590
But we did learn more about some of their preferences.
但是我们确实了解了更多关于他们的喜好,

5
00:00:16,591 --> 00:00:17,676
Like what?
好比什么?

6
00:00:17,677 --> 00:00:19,510
For instance,in the newsstand.
举例, 在报刊架上.

7
00:00:19,511 --> 00:00:21,265
12% of all guests think 
12%的客人认为

8
00:00:21,266 --> 00:00:24,019
there should be more foreign newspapers and magazines.
那儿应该有更多的外国报纸和杂志。

9
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:25,156
I certainly agree.
我非常同意.

10
00:00:25,157 --> 00:00:28,125
28% would like to see more news magazines, 
28%想要看到更多新闻杂志, 

11
00:00:28,126 --> 00:00:29,958
and fewer fashion magazines.
和少一点的时尚杂志.

12
00:00:29,959 --> 00:00:33,876
26% would like to see more fashion and life style magazines,
26%想要看到更多时尚和生活方式杂志,

13
00:00:33,877 --> 00:00:34,986
and less news.
和更少的新闻杂志.

14
00:00:34,987 --> 00:00:36,749
I wonder who's who.
我想知道谁是谁?

15
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:38,184
Men and women.
男人和女人.

16
00:00:38,185 --> 00:00:40,297
Business travelers and vacationers?
商务旅游者和度假者吗?

17
00:00:40,298 --> 00:00:42,144
We can't tell from the numbers.
我们不能从数字上看出来.

18
00:00:42,145 --> 00:00:45,346
14% had no opinion about the newsstand.
14%没有意见 关于报刊架.

19
00:00:45,347 --> 00:00:47,849
9% think we should sell cold drinks.
9%认为我们应该出售冷饮.

20
00:00:47,850 --> 00:00:50,290
7% want a newsstand on every floor.
7%想要一个报刊架 在每层楼.

21
00:00:50,291 --> 00:00:53,101
And 4% don't know we have a newsstand.
4%不知道我们有个报刊架.

22
00:00:53,102 --> 00:00:54,299
How can they miss it?
他们怎么能错过它呢?

23
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:56,879
They're having too good a time to notice.
他们玩的太愉快了, 以至没注意到.


